---
layout: default
title: Archives for %str_month% %year%
---
.big_box#archive_box
  %h1== Archive for #{to_month(page.month)}, #{page.year}
  %p== If you want to be adventurous you can view the <a href="/#{page.year}">entire year</a> of posts or lack thereof.
  - page.archive_posts.sort { |a, b| a.date <=> b.date }.reverse.each do |post|
    .article
      .grid_7.alpha
        %h2.title== <a href="#{post.url}">#{post.title}</a>
        %span.full_date= post.date.strftime("%d %B %Y")
      .grid_2.omega
        .short_date
          %span.month= post.date.strftime('%b')
          %span.day= post.date.day